"title": "5334: health",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5334: health",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A state of physical and spiritual well-being, which Scripture declares to be possible only through faith in Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Salvation as spiritual health</h2>\n<h3>The need for salvation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:3\">PSA 38:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:7\">PSA 38:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:12-Matt9:13\">MAT 9:12–9:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:31-Luke5:32\">LUK 5:31–5:32</a></p>\n<h3>The promise of salvation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:2\">EXO 15:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:4-Ps32:5\">PSA 32:4–32:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:4\">PSA 149:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:9\">1TH 5:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11\">TIT 2:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:15\">2PE 3:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:10\">REV 12:10</a></p>\n<h3>The experience of salvation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:5-Ps13:6\">PSA 13:5–13:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:16\">PSA 91:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:14\">PSA 118:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:1-Isa12:3\">ISA 12:1–12:3</a></p>\n<h2>The importance of health</h2>\n<h3>Health is to be sought after</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:2\">3JN 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:15\">JER 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:6\">JHN 5:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:9\">JHN 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:23\">1TH 5:23</a></p>\n<h3>Health as a wish in greeting people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:6\">1SA 25:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam20:9\">2SA 20:9</a></p>\n<h3>Health promised by God to his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:6\">JER 33:6</a></strong></p>\n<h3>A cause for praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:31\">MAT 15:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:9-Acts4:12\">ACT 4:9–4:12</a></p>\n<h2>The pursuit of health</h2>\n<h3>Hygiene</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:13\">DEU 23:13</a></p>\n<h3>Care of the body</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:18-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:18–6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:20-Prov4:22\">PRO 4:20–4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:34\">ACT 27:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:13\">ROM 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:24-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:24–9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:29\">EPH 5:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:7-1Tim4:8\">1TI 4:7–4:8</a></p>\n<h3>The balance of work and rest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:21\">EXO 34:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:8-Exod20:11\">EXO 20:8–20:11</a></p>\n<h2>Mental health</h2>\n<h3>State of the natural mind</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:6-Rom8:7\">ROM 8:6–8:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:18\">COL 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Mental disorder</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:28\">DEU 28:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:14-1Sam16:15\">1SA 16:14–16:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:28-Dan4:37\">DAN 4:28–4:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:20\">JHN 10:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:25\">ACT 26:25</a></p>\n<h3>An anxious mind</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:1\">JOB 10:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:10\">JER 15:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:41\">LUK 10:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:34\">LUK 21:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:17\">LUK 24:17</a></p>\n<h3>Anxiety resulting from judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:65\">DEU 28:65</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:34\">DEU 28:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:4\">ZEC 12:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:28\">ROM 1:28</a></p>\n<h3>The healthy mind</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:6\">PSA 42:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:25\">PRO 12:25</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37\">MAT 22:37</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:30\">MRK 12:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">LUK 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6-Phil4:8\">PHP 4:6–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:7\">1PE 5:7</a></p>",
